  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The investigators wish to study the effects of position changes during colonoscope insertion
      on patient comfort. The investigators hypothesize that early position changes would reduce
      colonoscope loop formation and patient discomfort.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
